                            <p>Alpha<sup>&reg;</sup> only accepts orders for shipments within the continental US. Orders to Alaska, Hawaii and international destinations will need to be done directly with Alpha<sup>&reg;</sup> Customer Service. E-mail to   <a href="mailto:info@alpha-tools.com">  info@alpha-tools.com</a> or call 800-648-7229 option 1.</p><h4>Expedited Shipping Rules</h4>
